             <h3 class="title">
              <a href="/news/firey-peachtree-city-car-wreck-claims-20-year-old-16-year-old">
               Police: Fiery Peachtree City car wreck claims lives of 2 teens
              </a>
             </h3>
            </header>
            <p>
             A 16-year-old and a 19-year-old were killed during a car crash Saturday evening, Peachtree City police say.

              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/gun-waiting-periods-rare-in-us-states-but-more-may-be-coming">
                Gun waiting periods rare in US states but more may be coming
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">

              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/video-shows-bystander-grabbing-mans-foot-after-he-falls-backward-off-of-balcony">
                Video shows bystander grabbing man’s foot after he falls backward off of balcony
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              A shocking video showed a man narrowly escaping serious injury or death after falling backward over a balcony thanks to a quick-thinking bystander who grabbed his foot.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/new-program-helps-shifts-unemployed-georgians-into-allied-health-careers">
                New program helps shift unemployed Georgians into allied health careers
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Lawrenceville resident Mylyn Ho is focused on her new career as an ophthalmic assistant and already has a full-time job lined up with an optometrist after she graduates in April from Ocuprep --an Allied Health training program that combines virtual and socially distant in-person instruction.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/women-would-rather-talk-about-death-than-money">
                Women would rather talk about death than money
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              You read that headline right. According to financial planner Beau Henderson of RichLife Advisors, 60 percent of women are more willing to discuss death than their finances.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-19T10:09:16-04:00">
              2 days ago
             </time>
             <!-- -->
            </div>
           </article>
           <article class="article post story-2" data-v-711e7e86="">

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/gop-us-rep-tom-reed-to-retire-after-sexual-misconduct-accusation">
                GOP US Rep. Tom Reed to retire after sexual misconduct accusation
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              U.S. Rep. Tom Reed, a Republican from western New York who was accused last week of rubbing a female lobbyist’s back and unhooking her bra without her consent in 2017, apologized to the woman on Sunday and announced that he will not run for reelection next year.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T21:26:39-04:00">
              3 hours ago
             </time>
             <!-- -->
            </div>
           </article>

              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/women-would-rather-talk-about-death-than-money">
                Women would rather talk about death than money
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              You read that headline right. According to financial planner Beau Henderson of RichLife Advisors, 60 percent of women are more willing to discuss death than their finances.
             </p>
